 <link>https://vse.la/stih/reklama-vedushchego-na-svadbu-v-stihah</link>
 <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-image field-type-image field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/stih/reklama-vedushchego-na-svadbu-v-stihah&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://vse.la/images/styles/thumb180/public/stihi_images/5971535008_18379006f8_w.jpg?itok=s2yPmQ30&quot; width=&quot;180&quot; height=&quot;120&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;–° –љ–µ–±–∞ –Ј–≤—С–Ј–і–Њ—З–Ї–∞ —А–Њ–љ—П–µ—В&lt;br /&gt;
–Э–µ–ґ–љ—Л–µ –ї—Г—З–Є —Б–≤–Њ–Є&lt;br /&gt;
–Ш —Б–µ—А–і—Ж–∞ —Б–Њ–µ–і–Є–љ—П–µ—В&lt;br /&gt;
–Ф–ї—П –±–Њ–ї—М—И–Њ–є-–±–Њ–ї—М—И–Њ–є –ї—О–±–≤–Є.&lt;br /&gt;
–Ш –≤–µ–і—С—В –і–Њ—А–Њ–≥–Њ–є —Б—З–∞—Б—В—М—П&lt;br /&gt;
–Ю—З–∞—А–Њ–≤–∞–љ–љ—Л—Е –ї—О–і–µ–є.&lt;br /&gt;
–Ь–Є—А —Б—В–∞–љ–Њ–≤–Є—В—Б—П –њ—А–µ–Ї—А–∞—Б–љ–µ–є,&lt;br /&gt;
–Ь–Є—А —Б—В–∞–љ–Њ–≤–Є—В—Б—П —А–Њ–і–љ–µ–є.&lt;br /&gt;
–°–∞–Љ—Л–є —П—А–Ї–Є–є, —Б–∞–Љ—Л–є –ї—Г—З—И–Є–є&lt;br /&gt;
–Я—А–∞–Ј–і–љ–Є–Ї —Б–≤–∞–і—М–±—Л –і–Њ —Г—В—А–∞ -&lt;br /&gt;
–Ы—Г—З—И–Є–є —Б–≤–∞–і–µ–±–љ—Л–є –≤–µ–і—Г—Й–Є–є&lt;br /&gt;
–Т—Б—С –Њ—Д–Њ—А–Љ–Є—В –љ–∞ —Г—А–∞!&lt;/p&gt;

